01:24:49.610 --> 01:25:06.579
Raúl Kripalani: pre-aggregated at source, with this proposal, we could potentially see a reduction factor of 2x on the wire, and I'll go into… into what that could potentially translate into. So just to kind of, like, give an overview of where the network is sitting today, there is…

561
01:25:06.580 --> 01:25:11.980
Raúl Kripalani: We have 890,000 validators, as of this morning.

